@page "/reports"

<PageTitle>Bao cao</PageTitle>

<section class="page-header-card">
    <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Reporting</p>
        <h1>Bao cao, canh bao va suc khoe van hanh</h1>
        <p>Quan sat toc do xu ly ho so, ty le ky thanh cong va hop dong sap het han.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-grid">
    <article class="stat-card compact"><span class="stat-label">Ty le ky thanh cong</span><strong>84%</strong><p>+6% so voi thang truoc</p></article>
    <article class="stat-card compact"><span class="stat-label">Thoi gian xu ly TB</span><strong>3.8 ngay</strong><p>Muc tieu 4.5 ngay</p></article>
    <article class="stat-card compact"><span class="stat-label">Hop dong den han</span><strong>11</strong><p>Can nhac truoc 30 ngay</p></article>
    <article class="stat-card compact"><span class="stat-label">Ti le ho so dung SLA</span><strong>91%</strong><p>Canh bao som cho 9 ho so</p></article>
</section>

<section class="panel-card">
    <div class="panel-header">
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Canh bao</p>
            <h3>Danh sach uu tien can xu ly</h3>
        </div>
    </div>

    <table class="admin-table">
        <thead>
            <tr><th>Loai</th><th>Noi dung</th><th>Muc do</th><th>Han xu ly</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>Hop dong</td><td>4 hop dong sap het han trong 7 ngay</td><td><span class="status-pill warning">Can chu y</span></td><td>08/06/2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Ho so</td><td>3 ho so dang qua SLA tham dinh phap ly</td><td><span class="status-pill critical">Gap</span></td><td>Hom nay</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Cong no</td><td>2 doi tac cham doi soat thanh toan</td><td><span class="status-pill info">Theo doi</span></td><td>10/06/2026</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</section>
